        "id": "comment",
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# ⚔️ Model Arena\n\nOne brief, three frontier models, side by side. The same prompt fans out to **OpenAI GPT-5 mini**, **Anthropic Claude Sonnet 5**, and **Google Gemini 3.5 Flash** — each answers in the same structure, so you compare reasoning, not formatting.\n\n**Differentiator:** a fan-out a chat box can't do — run one question against three providers in a single pass and read the answers next to each other.\n\n**Try this:** paste any decision, spec, or judgement call into the brief, then swap the model on any lane to build your own bracket."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": 40,
            "y": -280
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 540,
          "height": 230,
          "title": null,
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
