          "value": "Should a 12-person B2B SaaS startup build its own customer-facing analytics dashboard, or integrate a third-party embedded-analytics vendor, for its reporting feature? Ship target is one quarter out.",
          "description": "The question, spec, or decision every model should answer"
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": 50,
            "y": 60
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
